description:
All Schwarzkopf products available IN STORE ONLY. Store pre-orders and pick up is available. Contact your CanRad Sales Consultant or Customer Service for assistance.

DESCRIPTION
The BLONDME Lightener and Colour range provide the high performance needed to create personalized blonde looks. It is specially formulated to partner BLONDME bleach and colour shades. What it does: Premium Care Developer offer up to 9 levels of lift while the readytouse toners and white blending shades give endless creative potential for blonde hair. Its an oil developer formula that maintains hair's natural moisture to ensure your blondes have brilliant shine and a wonderfully soft feel to their hair.

FEATURES
Lifts on natural base 6 7
Premium hair developer
Oilin formula
Maintains the hair's natural moisture balance
Smooths the hair surface

HOW TO USE
Mix the developer with the BlondMe Bond Enforcing Powder using the proper ratio.
Section the hair.
Apply on small section of hair at a time.
Leave out 1.5 centimeters from the scalp.
Use plenty of product to insure full saturation.
Use the remaining product on the roots.
Rinse thoroughly.
Shampoo with BLONDME Keratin Restore Bonding Shampoo.
Apply toner as desired.

product_name: 120ml Miracle Coily Leave In 4oz Its a 10 CR12
description:
DESCRIPTION
It's a Ten Miracle Coily Leave In works well for naturally curly, wavy, twisted or braided styles to air-dry with more definition and is also a great choice for protection when heat styling.

FEATURES
1. Enhances natural curls
2. Restores shine
3. Defines curls
4. Defrizzes and tames fly-aways
5. Instant detangling
6. Creates silkiness
7. Nourishes hair
8. Lightweight formula
9. Helps reduce breakage
10. Thermal protector

HOW TO USE
Spray on hair after shower to detangle and style – use approximately 3-4 sprays for shoulder length hair (adjust based on your hairs length). Or, on dry hair to give a pick-me-up; mist entire lengths of strands and scrunchtwist to reignite your curls.

product_name: 300ml Miracle Coily Hydrating Shampoo 10oz Its a 10 CR12
description:
DESCRIPTION
It's a Ten Miracle Coily Hydrating Shampoo replenishes hair and deeply conditions. Improves hair quality, softness, smoothness and vitality.

FEATURES
1. Designed for curly and textured hair
2. Removes product buildup
3. Defines curls
4. Defrizzes and tames fly-aways
5. Helps reduce split ends
6. Moisturizing formula
7. Nourishes hair
8. Lightweight formula
9. Rich and creamy lather
10. Provides UV protection

HOW TO USE
Apply to wet hair. Massage thoroughly from scalp to ends. Rinse out thoroughly.

product_name: 118ml Miracle Coily Curl Cream 4oz Its a 10 CR12 FP
description:
DESCRIPTION
It's a Ten Miracle Coily Curl Cream helps your curls bring out their shine, any time, with an easy-to-use, lightweight cream that goes on damp and dries to sheer perfection. With It’s a 10 Miracle Coily Curl Cream, curls stay bouncy, smooth, and defined without being hard or crunchy.

FEATURES
1. Soft firm touchabel hold
2. Ultra bouncy curl definition
3. Ultimate defrizzer
4. Controls texture
5. Moisturizes
6. Imparts shine
7. Tames volume
8. Coconut and avocado oil infused
9. Helps reduce breakage and split ends
10. Great for twisting hold

HOW TO USE
Apply evenly to clean damp hair from roots to ends–do not rinse. Shape curls, air dry or diffuse to style. Can re-apply to dry hair to revitalize curls.

product_name: 148ml Miracle Coily Gelled Oil 5oz Its a 10 CR12
description:
DESCRIPTION
It's a Ten Miracle Coily Gelled Oil creates gorgeous frizz-free style without weight, greasiness, or crunch, with this weightless gel that conditions and improves the health of hair to tame curls, waves, and even straight styles with fewer flyaways and more sleekness.

FEATURES
1. Weightless curl definition
2. Enhanced shine
3. Soft and touchabel curls
4. Helps reduce split ends
5. Ultimate frizz control
6. Helps increase strength
7. Excellent braid control
8. Smoothes scalp
9. Medium hold
10. Nourishing formula

HOW TO USE
On wet, clean hair, apply enough to evenly distribute throughout the hair. Air dry or diffuse for perfect curls or blow dry straight. Curl with iron for shiny bouncy style. Or braid hair with extra control and shine.

product_name: 240ml Miracle Coily Mask 8oz Its a 10 CR12
description:
DESCRIPTION
It's a Ten Miracle Coily Mask powerfully restores and is an excellent conditioning treatment that literally coats hair from root to tip in revitalizing moisture. The hair shaft is fortified with nutrients and essential vitamins, making it strong and in better shape to resist damage.

FEATURES
1. Intense hydration
2. Provides humidity control

product_name: BlondMe Bond Enforcing Premium Lift 9 Lightener 450g CR6
description:
All Schwarzkopf products available IN STORE ONLY. Store pre-orders and pick up is available. Contact your CanRad Sales Consultant or Customer Service for assistance.

DESCRIPTION

Blondme Bond Enforcing Premium Lightener 9 is a high performance powder lightener. This is the first powder lightener to provide up to 9 levels of lift on natural and coloured hair. It offers perfect neutralisation thanks to it's antiyellowagents which directly target the pheomelanin in hair to avoid unwanted warm or yellow undertones.

FEATURES
Integrated bonding technology
Up to 9 levels of lift
Helps to protect the hair fiber during development for minimized hair breakage
Antiyellow agents to neutralize any warm undertones
Flexible mixing ratio
Easy workable consistency
Suitable for all technique

HOW TO USE
Always use in combination with BLONDME® Premium Developers.
Mix 1:1.5 to 1:2.5 (Ex: 30g BLONDME Premium Lightener 9 and 4575 mL BLONDME Premium Developer).
OnScalp Application : BLONDME Premium Developer 2 (7 Vol.) or 6 (20 Vol.).
Application : BLONDME Premium Developer 9 (30 Vol.).
Apply to dry hair and let develop for 20 to 45 minutes.
Additional heat is not recommended.
Visually check progress during development time.

PROTIP
For gentle lightening and optimal time control, use BLONDME Premium Developer 2 (7 Vol.).
Check visually every 5 minutes.

product_name: BlondMe Bond Enforcing Clay Lightener 350g CR6
description:
All Schwarzkopf products available IN STORE ONLY. Store pre-orders and pick up is available. Contact your CanRad Sales Consultant or Customer Service for assistance.

DESCRIPTION
This claybased powder lightener allows a precise application. The creamy consistency allows a smooth application and a seamless result. Thanks to the creamtosolid formula, the upper layer hardens and traps the moisture to ensure optimal lightening while protecting the rest of the hair from transfer.

FEATURES
Claybased lightener
With bond enforcing technology
Perfect for freehand lightening service
Up to 7 level of lift
Softtosolid formula

HOW TO USE
Use with the BlondMe Premium Developper
Ratio of 1: 1.5 or 1: 2 depending on the desired consistency
Apply on dry hair without additional heat

product_name: BlondMe Bond Enforcing Premium Lift 9 Lightener 450g CR6
description:
All Schwarzkopf products available IN STORE ONLY. Store pre-orders and pick up is available. Contact your CanRad Sales Consultant or Customer Service for assistance.

DESCRIPTION

Blondme Bond Enforcing Premium Lightener 9 is a high performance powder lightener. This is the first powder lightener to provide up to 9 levels of lift on natural and coloured hair. It offers perfect neutralisation thanks to it's antiyellowagents which directly target the pheomelanin in hair to avoid unwanted warm or yellow undertones.

FEATURES
Integrated bonding technology
Up to 9 levels of lift
Helps to protect the hair fiber during development for minimized hair breakage
Antiyellow agents to neutralize any warm undertones
Flexible mixing ratio
Easy workable consistency
Suitable for all technique

HOW TO USE
Always use in combination with BLONDME® Premium Developers.
Mix 1:1.5 to 1:2.5 (Ex: 30g BLONDME Premium Lightener 9 and 4575 mL BLONDME Premium Developer).
OnScalp Application : BLONDME Premium Developer 2 (7 Vol.) or 6 (20 Vol.).
Application : BLONDME Premium Developer 9 (30 Vol.).
Apply to dry hair and let develop for 20 to 45 minutes.
Additional heat is not recommended.
Visually check progress during development time.

PROTIP
For gentle lightening and optimal time control, use BLONDME Premium Developer 2 (7 Vol.).
Check visually every 5 minutes.

description:

DESCRIPTION
The BLONDME Lightener and Colour range provide the high performance needed to create personalized blonde looks. It is specially formulated to partner BLONDME bleach and colour shades. What it does: Premium Care Developer offer up to 9 levels of lift while the readytouse toners and white blending shades give endless creative potential for blonde hair. Lifts on natural base 6 7
Premium hair developer
Oilin formula

Smooths the hair surface

Section the hair.

DESCRIPTION
Schwarzkopf Igora Royal Permanent colour provides total coverage and intensity while maintaining scalp comfort. Its formula allows to equalize the colour evenly even on porous hair. The pigment penetrates the hair efficiently and is locked in for longlasting, vibrant colour.

FEATURES
Permanent hair colour.
Covers white air up to 100.
Longlasting colour retention.
Intense colour vibrancy.
Works even on porous hair.
Absolute truetotuft results.

HOW TO USE
Mix the colour and developer at a ratio of 1: 1 for a normal colouring, or 1: 2 for a lighter shade.
VIRGIN HAIR: apply the mixture to lengths and ends, then to roots after 15 to 20 minutes.
COLOURED HAIR: apply the mixture to the regrowth, then to the lengths and tips after 15 to 30 minutes.
Leave as directed on instructions.
Rinse thoroughly, then wash and condition the hair.

DESCRIPTION
Schwarzkopf Igora Royal Permanent colour provides total coverage and intensity while maintaining scalp comfort. Its formula allows to equalize the colour evenly even on porous hair. The pigment penetrates the hair efficiently and is locked in for longlasting, vibrant colour.

FEATURES
Permanent hair colour.
Covers white air up to 100.
Longlasting colour retention.
Intense colour vibrancy.
Works even on porous hair.
Absolute truetotuft results.

HOW TO USE
Mix the colour and developer at a ratio of 1: 1 for a normal colouring, or 1: 2 for a lighter shade.
VIRGIN HAIR: apply the mixture to lengths and ends, then to roots after 15 to 20 minutes.
COLOURED HAIR: apply the mixture to the regrowth, then to the lengths and tips after 15 to 30 minutes.
Leave as directed on instructions.
Rinse thoroughly, then wash and condition the hair.

BB Brown Booster Color High Power Igora Royal

All Schwarzkopf products available IN STORE ONLY. Store pre-orders and pick up is available. Contact your CanRad Sales Consultant or Customer Service for assistance.

DESCRIPTION
Schwarzkopf Igora Royal Permanent colour provides total coverage and intensity while maintaining scalp comfort. Its formula allows to equalize the colour evenly even on porous hair. The pigment penetrates the hair efficiently and is locked in for longlasting, vibrant colour.

FEATURES
Permanent hair colour.
Covers white air up to 100.
Longlasting colour retention.
Intense colour vibrancy.
Works even on porous hair.
Absolute truetotuft results.

HOW TO USE
Mix the colour and developer at a ratio of 1: 1 for a normal colouring, or 1: 2 for a lighter shade.
VIRGIN HAIR: apply the mixture to lengths and ends, then to roots after 15 to 20 minutes.
COLOURED HAIR: apply the mixture to the regrowth, then to the lengths and tips after 15 to 30 minutes.
Leave as directed on instructions.
Rinse thoroughly, then wash and condition the hair.

product_name: BlondMe 800 Gram Bond Enforcing Premium Lightener Lift 9
description:
All Schwarzkopf products available IN STORE ONLY. Store pre-orders and pick up is available. Contact your CanRad Sales Consultant or Customer Service for assistance.

DESCRIPTION

Blondme Bond Enforcing Premium Lightener 9 is a high performance powder lightener. This is the first powder lightener to provide up to 9 levels of lift on natural and coloured hair. It offers perfect neutralisation thanks to it's antiyellowagents which directly target the pheomelanin in hair to avoid unwanted warm or yellow undertones.

FEATURES
Integrated bonding technology
Up to 9 levels of lift
Helps to protect the hair fiber during development for minimized hair breakage
Antiyellow agents to neutralize any warm undertones
Flexible mixing ratio
Easy workable consistency
Suitable for all technique

HOW TO USE
Always use in combination with BLONDME® Premium Developers.
Mix 1:1.5 to 1:2.5 (Ex: 30g BLONDME Premium Lightener 9 and 4575 mL BLONDME Premium Developer).
OnScalp Application : BLONDME Premium Developer 2 (7 Vol.) or 6 (20 Vol.).
Application : BLONDME Premium Developer 9 (30 Vol.).
Apply to dry hair and let develop for 20 to 45 minutes.
Additional heat is not recommended.
Visually check progress during development time.

PROTIP
For gentle lightening and optimal time control, use BLONDME Premium Developer 2 (7 Vol.).
Check visually every 5 minutes.
